  "texts": [
    "A brief description of the TS to be generated is required to explicitly tell the LLM about the coverage of specific context or conditions in the generated TS (e.g., \"Delivery with Rücksendung Ausland\" in Fig. 1).",
    "While LLMs also allow the generation of TSs without any description, such generated TSs can be very generic.",
    "In our preliminary experiments with Austrian Post Group IT (authors), we further observed the varying efficacy of LLMs in generating TSs based on the richness and specificity of the input.",
    "This has implications for the extent of manual intervention required in the final TS generation.",
    "Hence, RAGTAG requires a brief yet specific description of the TS to be generated."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}